config_create_nft_wallet_description: If it is active, when a new user registers or detects an account without a wallet, it generates a wallet.
config_ default_funding_amount_descripti: Amount of Matic to recharge. When there is a wallet without funds, generate a Matic tx.
config_max_qualifications_description: Maximum number of qualifications to be taken into account to calculate whether to grant a badge to a business
config_min_qualifications_description: Minimum number of qualifications, in case of not reaching the maximum number, that are necessary to calculate whether to grant a badge to a business
config_threshold_description: Minimum percentage of positive ratings that the quality of a business must obtain for it to receive the badge.
config_c2b_tab_participa_description: Section to view the active challenges of the platform and the rewards you have won
config_map_badges_filter_status_descript: Show/Hide the qualities filter of the app map. This filter returns the businesses that have the badge of the selected quality
config_qualifications_system_status_desc: Activate/Deactivate the system to qualify the qualities of a business after each purchase.
config_profile_pis_status_description: Show/Hide the Paraula, Impuls and Sabiessa statistics from the user profile on the “Connecta” platform.
